STATE
v.
Tony Jeffrey CABLE. No. 340P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 23, 2007. Robert Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, Ronald L. Moore, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th day of July 2007 by Defendant for Petition for Plain Error Review Pursuant to N.C.G.S. 7A-29:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 23rd day of August 2007."
